Binary Tree -
      10
     /  \
    20   30
   /    /  \
  40   50   60

Binary Search Tree -
      4
     / \
    2   6
   / \ / \
  1  3 5  7

TRAVERSALS -

        1
       / \
      2   3
     / \   \
    4   5   6

Pre-Order (Root → Left → Right):
1 2 4 5 3 6
USE -
Clone or Copy a Tree

In-Order (Left → Root → Right):
4 2 5 1 3 6
USE -
In-order traversal of a BST gives values in ascending order (Sorted Output)

Post-Order (Left → Right → Root):
4 5 2 6 3 1
USE -
Delete a Tree (Bottom-Up)